Kiighwyaq

Iimnanguq yuuk nuliilek avaqutiilnguq salin.
Mughunniighaqelghii naqamunangaqelghii.
Ilangani maaten mughulluni aghtuumalghii.
Qenwat unugumakanga.
Quulmun esghaghyalghiimi kiighwyaq esghaamakanga.
Esghaghyaqenni kiighwyaneng mengteghiitnim aga ifkaghtuq kenghhaq.
Legan nekevluni taglaamalghii.
Kaalluni iteghyalghnmi nulighha aqsangumalghii.
Neghulluteng qavaamalghiit.

Unaami yuuk mughusimalghii.
Unangluni neghsameng tagiyalghiimi nulighha ighniimalghii mekelghiighmeng.
Ugingan aghnam atiimakanga, Kiighwyameng.
Qavaghhiinaghqun anglimalghii.
Aghnaghaq aqsanglaataamalghii.
Ighniyalghiimi aghnaghaghmeng.
Taagken kenlanga alla aghnaq aqsangnaniimalghii taaqumalghii.
Tawani nunaami kiyaghsimalghiit.

Qenwat aghnaghaq anglighllagumalghii ama mekelghiiqlu taana.
Maaten ilangani atangat mughulluni iikusimakanga.
Ima tuqumalghii.
Naangatugiminengnagaquulluni tuqusimalghii ellmineng.
Mekelghiighem nayani pimakanga, "Atanka naanka tuqulaghaatut.
Sumeghtaghaghaquten entaqun temngi nunamenniluki.
Whaa uum kenlenganeng aqnighpenani tuqukaq kaapluni kanaghluni meghqulluni taana kiighwyamun mayughaquq.
Aga ataput naaput mayumaat."

Mekelghiiq unugyagu aanluni tapghaq quulmun miluusaqenni kiighwyakun agaamalghii.
Taaggun tapghaghqun mayuumalghii.
Kaasami aghqutaallghiinun1 ilasimalghii repall teghigniqem puyguluku nayani.
Qesiqun uksughqughaquq.
Tamakut kiighwyat taana mekelghiiq umiilgughtesimakangat.
Qesiqun aanyan mengteghamineng salin nunamelluku yuget ilangita qemisimaat.
Llaaghanwha mayuumalghii.
Ama yuuk kaapegkaq, qemitkaq, suflugaqaq sangami tuqurakegtaqa?
Qayughllag'qun kiighwyani aghqutaallghiini teghigniqem puywaaqelghiit yuget unguvalleghqateng.

Qamagtuq.
Tefaay.
